I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
ANY MORE OBSCENITIES, NO
MORE NAME-CALUING, NO
KICKING, BITING, SPITTING
OR FIGHTING..
SO, NEXT TINE
TELL YOUR PARENTS
STAY HOME!
ⓒ 2009 . STEVEN G . ARTLEY
